  • Constructor Details

    • User

      public User(long id, String username, String password, Date registerDate, Date lastLogin, long phoneNumber)
      Constructs a user object with the specified values.
      Parameters:
      id - the unique id of the user
      username - the username of the user. Cannot be null or blank.
      password - the password of the user. Cannot be null or blank.
      registerDate - the date when the user registered. Cannot be null.
      phoneNumber - the phone number of the user. Cannot be negative.
      Throws:
      IllegalArgumentException - if the username is null or blank, the password is null or blank, the register date is null, the phone number is negative or the budget is null.
